headline: GE Stock Hits Its First All-Time High in Decades. It Took 9,150 Days.
summary: It took 9,150 days, but  GE  Aerospace stock hit a new all-time high.  GE, which is now GE Aerospace, last hit an intraday high of $289.54 on Aug. 28, 2000, according to Dow Jones Market Data.  Back then, Janet Jackson and N’Sync topped Billboard charts.
